{"tid":1066712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個賤女人害我屋企，好彩有巴打幫我起咗佢底","createTime":"2019-03-18T05:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T11:18:05.000Z","uid":18911,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f50af984bb2821c0d3475ede0f0fc9e4a594cb53","tid":1066712,"uid":18911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"有個賤女人 害到我屋企又冇，老母臨老都要搞離婚，<br />\n老母差啲有精神病，<br />\n之前都post過 想大大既連登仔好心幫下我 起個女人底<br />\n點知被人屌 報仇都要人幫 <br />\n<br />\n老實講 我一個小小既廢j 又冇咩方法搵到個賤女人<br />\n想起人底，但自己又無能為力 <br />\n眼白白睇住老母被個賤女人害<br />\n其實我自己都被佢間接咁害到我既生活差咗<br />\n但個賤女人一定好有成功感 <br />\n呢種女人專搵有家庭既男人 害嗰個家庭<br />\n但我就報唔到仇<br />\n嗰種無奈 失落 同挫敗感 有冇人明啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩 正義撚巴打 (個fd) 幫我起左佢底<br />\n佢係收錢既，但見我咁慘 先幫下我 唔收錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWaG0PH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWaG0PH.png&h=1ae808b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vjk7Wn3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjk7Wn3.png&h=5ffc8595&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOe4YBp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOe4YBp.png&h=a122bc24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同我差唔多經歷既人 或者想起人底既 可以搵巴打幫幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hdhajjsvd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhdhajjsvd&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4My3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=c106770a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hdhajjsvd</a>"},{"pid":"9dac83c19e2e06efa6f0c542c44f7e6e6a1dc518","tid":1066712,"uid":18911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以幫我起呢個女人底？想報仇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/942450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/942450</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n以前個post 冇人幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88667444a0db6ac22c96e785a9e681efdc2b58be","tid":1066712,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"J圖呢"},{"pid":"e3430791e92e8417ca0a63e5f808f126c8b32977","tid":1066712,"uid":141176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cb8d4b0fa439f4864de92c7bdd9b4438766aa3","tid":1066712,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8323c2408099018603d582dc568ecd8f2d9f9770","tid":1066712,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"無啦？詳情呢"},{"pid":"2a9eda2818b7be257453ac60b96b8ae9300f61c7","tid":1066712,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"連登家庭法庭"},{"pid":"6638df837125c3fd5683a3ab94ad49040771829b","tid":1066712,"uid":167506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"留返啲時間做其他野好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626637ada4449a349dfee3db10a78c5410e344df","tid":1066712,"uid":18911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:51:40.000Z","msg":"詳情#2有link<br />\n我以前講過啦<br />\n不過都可以再講既<br />\n佢地行山識<br />\n就係個女人搭上我老豆<br />\n搞到屋企離婚<br />\n有行山友話我知，個賤女人專搵有家庭既男人<br />\n之前都搵過另一個行山友，只係人地冇理佢<br />\n就搵上我老頭"},{"pid":"984e703beb3192da9190a3e03187e004f336c53e","tid":1066712,"uid":18911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>詳情#2有link<br />\n我以前講過啦<br />\n不過都可以再講既<br />\n佢地行山識<br />\n就係個女人搭上我老豆<br />\n搞到屋企離婚<br />\n有行山友話我知，個賤女人專搵有家庭既男人<br />\n之前都搵過另一個行山友，只係人地冇理佢<br />\n就搵上我老<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">豆</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"dd29c1190a1539079cab2ca1e139c49663a2ea03","tid":1066712,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:02:28.000